{"tid":1331530,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老實說，一毛二毛唔毛甚至十毛都唔會夠我地玩！","createTime":"2019-07-19T03:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T04:37:28.000Z","uid":201552,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f7d93fd06ae7b7247d037a91158da16afae6603c","tid":1331530,"uid":201552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:25:27.000Z","msg":"我地做得連仔就預左要團結一致！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />槍口對外不對內<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，班鳩毛點玩都好，玩零晨開po洗又好乜都好，諗深一層係佢地on9姐，有覺唔訓做埋d無謂嘢，收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地一樣可以朝早精精神神咁推翻d正氣po上去熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我好有信心咁話比大家聽！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地連仔絕不分化，不互屌。錯左就認，錯左就改，就系咁簡單！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申中學生一名，借ac<br />\n我都可以咁有信心，各位巴絲都一定得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721 見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">勿忙</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">初衷</span></span>"},{"pid":"53d1a83ae148a52798780ac91f43817266a49e2a","tid":1331530,"uid":201552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:26:18.000Z","msg":"Sor9ry 打錯，係五毛先岩"},{"pid":"abe3f710ec0bbd4547ccff2776d4eb099fd4009b","tid":1331530,"uid":201552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53d1a83ae148a52798780ac91